headline: Union Pacific CEO explains delay in revised merger filing
summary: Union Pacific delayed its revised merger application with Norfolk Southern after regulators clarified data formatting requirements, its CEO said. The post Union Pacific CEO explains delay in revised merger filing appeared first on FreightWaves.
